<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<% include ../partials/head.ejs %>

  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="body-wrapper">
        <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>
          <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
            <% results.forEach(function(r) { %>
              <div class="upgrade-content">
                <div class="content-wrapper">
                  <p class="large">Your Sandbox
                    <strong>
                      <%= r.org_id  %>
                    </strong> is a
                    <%= r.org_type  %> Instance,
                      <br/>on
                      <%= r.external_rel_name  %>
                  </p>
                  <h3>What would you like information on?</h3>
                  <p class="upgrade-option" id="upgrade">Upgrade to Summer '18
                    <br />(get the Preview)</p>
                  <div class="component upgrade-info" id="upgrade">
                    <% if (r.org_type == "PREVIEW") { %>
                      <!-- replace text below with dynamic data from CSV file -->
                      <p>
                        <strong>No action is needed</strong> as your Sandbox is already on a Preview Instance</p>
                      <p>If you need to refresh for other reasons, do so well in advance of 11:59pm PT on May 4, 2018 (7:59
                        UTC on May 5, 2018) to make sure your Sandbox completes before the deadline. If you refresh after
                        the deadline or your Sandbox doesn't complete in time, it will be built on a Non-Preview Instance.</p>

                      <% } %>
                        <% if (r.org_type == "NON-PREVIEW") { %>
                          <!-- replace text below with dynamic data from CSV file -->
                          <p>To get the preview, we require you to refresh to a Sandbox instance that will be upgraded early
                            to Summer '18.
                          </p>

                          <p>
                            <strong>Please refresh well in advance of 11:59p.m. PT on May 4, 2018 (07:59 UTC on May 5, 2018)</strong>.
                            If you refresh after the deadline or your Sandbox doesn't complete in time, it will be built
                            on a Non-Preview instance.
                          </p>

                          <% } %>
                  </div>
                  <p class="upgrade-option" id="stay">Stay on Spring '18
                    <br />(no Preview)</p>
                  <div class="component upgrade-info" id="stay">
                    <% if (r.org_type == "PREVIEW") { %>
                      <!-- replace text below with dynamic data from CSV file -->
                      <p>To stay on Spring '18, we require you to refresh to a Non-Preview Sandbox Instance.</p>
                      <p>
                        <strong>Please wait and refresh after 12:00am PT on May 5, 2018 (8:00 UTC on May 5, 2018).</strong> If you
                        refresh before this date, your Sandbox may be built on a Preview Instance.</p>

                      <% } %>
                        <% if (r.org_type == "NON-PREVIEW") { %>
                          <!-- replace text below with dynamic data from CSV file -->
                          <p>
                            <strong>No action is needed</strong> as your Sandbox is already on a Non-Preview Instance</p>
                          <p>If you need to refresh for other reasons, please wait and refresh after 12:00 a.m. PT on May 5,
                            2018 (8:00 UTC on May 5, 2018) to remain on a Non-Preview Instance.</p>

                          <% } %>
                  </div>
                  <p class="large">
                    <strong>Note: </strong> If you decide to stay on the current Winter ‘18 release, your Sandbox will not be upgraded
                    to Spring ‘18 until February 10, 2018.</p>
                  <% }); %>
                    <div class="component">
                      <div class="divider"></div>
                      <div class="helpful-links">
                        <h4>Additional Information</h4>
                        <p>Get more in-depth information about the Sandbox Preview on the
                          <a href="https://www.salesforce.com/blog/2017/12/salesforce-spring-18-sandbox-preview-instructions"
                            target="_blank">Salesforce Blog</a>.</p>
                        <p>Watch a video on
                          <a href="http://salesforce.vidyard.com/watch/dzC5Xx9GF8dJEM8wUqGim5" target="_blank">Demystifying Sandbox Preview</a>.</p>
                        <p>For more resources, to ask questions and engage with experts around release readiness, please join
                          the
                          <a href="http://www.salesforce.com/success-releasereadiness" target="_blank"> Release Readiness &amp; Feature Adoption</a> group in the Trailblazer Community.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
        <% include ../partials/script_section.ejs %>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>